divs: sighting details11\30\12 11:02 pm on my way to pick up food at local vendor when i saw a triagular shaped object in the northeast sky with the center light much brighter than the other's .i stopped got out and took 2 photo's with my 4s i phone ,and continued on my way.when you zoom the photo ,the top right looks like lighting bolts going toward the object .i don't remember seeing any that night .
Summary: observed triangular shaped lights in sky, took photo's ,when zoomed it appear's as if lighting from top right of photo going to object
